channel.title: Turbo Penguin
channel.description:
Hey, can someone make a turbo penguin script it should be pretty easy but i cant keep on making it click the penguin. This is the game http://www.gamesheep.com/game/turbocharged-penguins/?PlayNow And this is my script it made to try to get it
// http://www.gamesheep.com/game/turbocharged-penguins/?PlayNow // by Yachibu program turbo; var x,y:integer; begin repeat if(findcolorTolerance(x,y,5598595,1,1,350,320,25)) or (findcolorTolerance(x,y,11438966,1,1,350,320,25)) or (findcolorTolerance(x,y,1050882,1,1,350,320,25)) or (findcolorTolerance(x,y,6518405,1,1,350,320,25)) or (findcolorTolerance(x,y,3887205,1,1,350,320,25)) then begin MoveMouse(x,y); clickmouse(x,y,true); end; until(iskeydown('q')) end.
